question: Sui chit kang-khu chok-phín tī i ê chú-iàu kiat-kó lāi-té, tit tio̍h siōng-koân ê tan-it pāi-hun-pí ki-chhó͘ ê piáu-hiān chí-piau?
Tī chia̍h tián-piau lāi-té, só͘-ū bêng-khak chí-chhut ê F1 kap Accuracy ê pah-hun-pī (percentage) phing-kin sī siáⁿ?
Sánn-ū tō-kang iōng 'sí-kè-pō· sin-bûn hun-sek hong-keh' chòe i-kù ê hong-hoat, i ê koan-kiān chhòng-sin sī siáⁿ-mih?
按照描述，哪一个项目是明确设计来分析随时间推移的事件的？表格中有什么证据支持这一点？
answer: ‘TRR’ 项目的设计是用于时间分析。这由它的名称 ('Temporal Reasoning')、它的关键创新 ('Temporal reasoning for crash detection') 以及它的主要结果 ('Superior crisis detection across multiple periods') 所支持。

question: 列出所有个创新或者方法有明文提着大语言模型 (LLMs) 或者基于代理系统个工作个名字。
Soe-ūi ê kang-chok tùi sím-mih lâi kóng, sī teh iōng sím-mih kāng-chè lâi chò in ê chhòng-sin he̍k-chiá sī hong-sek ê hūn-chú?
LLM-Annotator ê '29% improvement over crowdworkers', nā chìn-chêng ê crowdworker accuracy sī 60%, án-ne LLM-Annotator ê accuracy beh sī siáⁿ-mih?
Ū bô kàn-khòaⁿ kám-ū teh chún-chún ê koan-hē tī 'agent' ê hong-sek kap piau-té lāi-té ê 'Key Innovation'?
answer: Ū, ū chi̍t-khóaⁿ chheng-chhó ê koan-hē. 2 ê kang-chok kā agent tòe teh in ê hong-sek lāi-té, StockAgent kap EconAgent, lóng-chóng ū kòe chú-iàu ê ián-kiù sī teh tùi sím-mih lâi sím-mih ('Multi-LLM trading simulation' kap 'LLM-powered economic simulation'). Chit-ê hō͘ lâng kám-kak agent-based ê hong-sek tī chit-ê sò͘-kì-chi̍p lāi-té chú-iàu leh ēng-lâi chhòng-chō ho̍k-cha̍p hē-thóng ê sím-mih.

question: Siong-chi̍t ê kang-chok tī in ê chú-iàu kiat-kó lāi-té, ū pò-tō nn̄g-ê bô-kâng ê F1 hun-sò͘?
Pí-phí MACK kap FinReport ê chú-iàu sò͘-jī kiat-kó, MACK ê te̍k-tēng kiat-kó, nā-chún beh pí-kàu, ē-sái sǹg sī chi̍t-ê gōa-lâi-tiám (outlier) koh-chài-leh?
answer: MACK ê Word F1 hun-sò͘ 96.89% ē-sái sǹg sī chi̍t-ê gōa-lâi-tiám. I pí tē-it-ê piau-sī ê sò͘-tiāu kè-tiāu (MACK ê Event F1 81.33% kap FinReport ê Accuracy 75.40%) koh-khah-koân, piáu-bêng tī jī-chân ê jīm-bū si̍t-hiān ê hāu-lu̍t chin-chiàⁿ-si̍t koân, kap kî-thaⁿ, koh-khah ho̍k-cha̍p ê jīm-bū, chhiūⁿ sū-kiāⁿ chhái-chi̍p a̍h-sī tâu-chu hun-sek pí-kàu.
